{"tid":926008,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"易中天算唔算係中國文化研究員嘅第一人？","createTime":"2018-12-03T06:45:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T02:16:48.000Z","uid":125122,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b32e5e6c178f8222412ed1a0639a6e85e3a15c87","tid":926008,"uid":125122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T06:45:21.000Z","msg":"是咁的，早排見到強國有人吹奏依位大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話咩角度新穎，題材豐富<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁我即刻去拜讀下大作，結果真係睇到我五體投地，驚為天人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n    咁介紹下大師背景先啦，維基：易中天，湖南長沙人，作家。畢業於武漢大學文學碩士學位。現為廈門大學人文學院中文系教授、博士生導師。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 知乎：易中天在網絡上開創了一个非常好的風氣，就是評論歷史必須拿出原始史料作為依據。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n    廢話講完即刻去文睇下大師風采，以下內容擇錄於易中天中華史01:祖先第一章：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">女媧是一隻大青蛙...因為她原本是蛙。變成蛇是有人𥚃做了手腳。時間，不晚於漢。</span><br />\n<br />\n    咁你好自然會浮現左幾個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第一，點解係青蛙，有咩理據？第二，係邊個要將佢改成蛇身呢？改成蛇身嘅背後理由又係咩呢？第三，不晚於漢嘅理據係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係大師不愧就大師，全部問題都有解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">媧，今人讀蛙，古人讀呱，正是青蛙的聲音。可見媧就是蛙，女媧便是女蛙。</span><br />\n<br />\n哇...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你老味用普通話讀音黎解釋呀屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲唔係史上第一人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">因為蛇可以變成龍，蛙就不行。如果女媧是蛙，龍的傳人豈非成為蛙的傳人？</span><br />\n<br />\n因為為左自稱龍的傳人，想合理化佢，所以就改成蛇尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邏輯緊扣，脈絡清晰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然唔知點解唔係改成龍尾，又唔知點解古人都會有龍的傳人嘅身份認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所謂人頭蛇身的文字記載，最早見於東漢王逸的楚辭章句。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n漢朝有人頭蛇身嘅記載，但係女媧係蛙，咁自然佢係喺漢朝前就被人改左。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依然係咁無懈可擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n    話咁快睇完第一章，其實仲有啲精彩推論係到，不過暫時睇第二章：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">夏娃是女媧的前身。女媧有前身嗎？有，因為她是母親，或母親神。...人，總是先成為少女，再成為母親的。因此，女媧必有前身。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌佢老尾，係咪high 撚大左，大撚埋右。佢到底啪咗啲咩，可唔可以俾兩斤我試試<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然而大師都係有俾出理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解個前身唔係大師佢阿媽，又唔係大師佢阿爸，偏偏就係夏娃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能大家都估到，屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 夏「蛙」呀嘛。膚淺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">讀音接近倒在其次，更重要的是心靈的共通。</span><br />\n<br />\n心靈的共通。<br />\n心靈的共通。<br />\n心靈的共通。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">易中天在網絡上開創了一个非常好的風氣，就是評論歷史必須拿出原始史料作為依據。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n文章來源：<a href=\"http://m.99lib.net/book/4263/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.99lib.net%2Fbook%2F4263%2Findex.html&d=E19L6z%2Bp8GfveTtRqWmKGfM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=8559299b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.99lib.net/book/4263/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n注：殘體傷眼<br />\n<br />\n有人睇再同大家分析大師作品"},{"pid":"cc35c810e82409791b4ebb6bc1ffd5e41fb9a781","tid":926008,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T23:35:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢排睇《瀛涯勝覽》，諗起Gavin Menzies<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"594b1066e6f7822557a736865933f45adfcf004a","tid":926008,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T00:26:05.000Z","msg":"目前最早提及女媧既記載, 好似係長沙子彈庫楚帛書<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x9mv44s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx9mv44s.jpg&h=9c142ed5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fbfd25a5adcb640da69afb89b5a06eb281dcb768","tid":926008,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T01:08:14.000Z","msg":"唔寫小說嘥晒"},{"pid":"2325cb49d75b115be5ed48b3bafa3633d9a1426d","tid":926008,"uid":96617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T02:16:48.000Z","msg":"但睇佢個品三國系列真係唔錯<br />\n點解呢到好似失心瘋咁"}]}